            <bold>FIG. 3.</bold>
          </label>
          <caption>
            <p>A phylogenetic tree for all cluster motifs in the data set. The tree was created by using a distance matrix consisting of best similarity scores between motifs (Tran and Huang, <xref rid="B17" ref-type="bibr">2015</xref>). Motif ID is concatenated with motif name at the label of the tree.</p>
          </caption>
