  <sec id="s011">
    <title>4. Conclusion</title>
    <p>MOTIFSIM 2.1 web tool and command-line tool contain several technical improvements as well as additional features to further support the motif analysis. The new version allows combining similar motifs. It also supports the comparisons for the global significant motifs as well as every motif with motifs in a database. In addition, the relationship between motifs can be observed through the phylogenetic trees. MOTIFSIM 2.1 web tool and command-line tool including user manuals, test data sets, and test results are freely available at <uri xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://motifsim.org">http://motifsim.org</uri></p>
  </sec>
